subSubSection.paragraph:
This species occurs in a small area of arid fynbos on the acidic lithosol soils (Glenrosa and Mispah forms) of North Outeniqua Sandstone Fynbos vegetation 
(
FFs 18; 
Rebelo et al. 2006
). The plant grows along streams or near water in the valley bottom, but is also found higher up the lower slopes along seepages.
